---
layout: page
title: Products
---

<section class="py-16">
    <div class="inner">
        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row -mx-4 xl:-mx-8 mb-12">
            <div class="flex-1 px-4 md:px-8 mb-8">
                <h1 class="text-5xl text-red-700">Products</h1>
                <p>Just like our location in Krotz Springs, we offer you the best boudin, sausage, and specialty meats. Everything is made in house, ready for you to pick up and cook with. Browse our categories below to see what'll complement your next meal. 
            </div>
            <div class="flex-1 px-4 xl:px-8">
                <img
                    srcset="{{ "v1601937878/kartchners/tenderloin" | sizes("https://res.cloudinary.com/hmillerdev/image/upload/ar_1.3,c_crop/f_auto,q_80")}}" 
                    src="https://res.cloudinary.com/hmillerdev/image/upload/ar_1.3,c_crop/f_auto,q_80/v1601937878/kartchners/tenderloin"
                    alt="Well seasoned stuffed pork tenderloin on ice"
                />
            </div>
        </div>
        <hr class="mb-12"/>
        <ul class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-x-16 gap-y-6 max-w-5xl mb-16 mx-auto leading-tight">
            {% for product in collections.product %}
                <li>
                    <a href="{{ product.url }}">
                        <h2 class="text-3xl text-gray-900 hover:text-red-700 transition-colors duration-200">{{ product.data.title }}</h2>
                    </a>
                </li>
            {% endfor %}
        </ul>
    </div>
</div>
